in 1798 and 1800,

00:03:03.848 --> 00:03:09.601
and which put forward a theory
to the effect that nearly

00:03:09.601 --> 00:03:15.457
universal poverty was an
essential and inevitable fact of

00:03:15.457 --> 00:03:17.550
human existence.
 

00:03:17.550 --> 00:03:21.240
Thank God he was wrong.
 

00:03:21.240 --> 00:03:28.431
Third, we'll look at Gregory
Clarke's exploration of Malthus'

00:03:28.431 --> 00:03:29.389
world.
 

00:03:29.389 --> 00:03:32.960
Clarke is the author of
Farewell To Alms,

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:37.669
